OOC: Whoo hoo.  I'm back and only mostly red.

::Aerotaur::
    He nods to Grounded.  "I agree on all points.  With two conditions.  I 
will supervise all of Trinity's training and Deemos is mine to kill when we 
attack."  He stretches his wings and leans forward.  "We should be going 
soon."
